---
title: Toasted Rice Bowl with Shrimp, Sweet Corn, and Red Bell Pepper
description: Rice bowls are great, but toasted rice bowls are out of this world. There’s an irresistibly nutty flavor and textural contrast to this dish—not to mention a kick of spice from the chili, lime, and soy sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/toasted-shrimp-rice-bowl-4bddbce0.jpg
